# Workflow

1) Upload docx
- Frontend calls /api/upload
- Backend saves inputs_dir/{doc_id}.docx
- Backend extracts requirement.txt to outputs_dir/{doc_id}/

2) Decompose
- /api/decompose (lang=zh-CN/ja-JP/en-US supported)
- Runs backend/decompose_service.py and persists JSON

3) Schedule
- /api/schedule (lang supported)
- Runs backend/schedule_service.py and persists JSON

4) Estimate
- /api/estimate (lang supported)
- Runs backend/estimate_service.py and persists JSON

Cache key is doc_id + lang, so repeated runs reuse persisted artifacts.
